fields.description: This assignment covers an introduction to Coal, Petroleum, Natural Gas and Limited natural resources.
This assignment covers an introduction to Sexual Reproduction, Reproductive Organs, Fertilisation, Development of Embryo and Asexual Reproduction.

This assignment covers an introduction to Adolescence and Puberty, Changes at Puberty, Secondary Sexual Characters, Role of Hormones, Reproductive Phase of Life, Sex Determination and Reproductive Health.
This assignment covers an introduction to Generation of Force, Change of State of Motion, Change of Shape, Contact Forces, Non-Contact Forces and Pressure.
This assignment covers an introduction to Friction, Factors affecting friction, Necessity of Friction, Ways to Reduce and Increase friction and Fluid Friction.
This assignment covers an introduction to Sound, Vibration, Sound produced by Humans, Medium of Propogation, Human ear, Amplitude, Frequency, Audible and Inaudible sounds and Noise.

This assignment covers an introduction to The Moon, The Stars, Constellations, The Solar System, The sun, The Planets, Asteroids, Comets and Satellites.
